0xDB1EA9411C8911EC// N_0xdb1ea9411c8911ec
void 0xDB1EA9411C8911EC(int checkpointHandle);Parameters:checkpointHandle: the handle of a created checkpointNativeDB Introduced: v1180This native is used for the "larger" circular checkpoints, and sets the circle/ring around the checkpoint to point in the same direction as the inner arrow
